Fightful reports that Jimmy Uso has been sidelined with an undisclosed injury. The specifics of the injury remain undisclosed, leaving fans and the wrestling community speculating about the nature and severity of the setback.

While injuries are an unfortunate reality in the world of professional wrestling, fans are hopeful for a speedy recovery for Jimmy Uso and eagerly anticipate his return to the squared circle. Until then, the wrestling world will continue to monitor updates on his condition and eagerly await his eventual comeback.

Stay tuned for further updates as Jimmy Uso's recovery journey progresses, and let's all send our best wishes for a swift and complete recovery to one-half of one of WWE's most beloved tag teams.